{"tid":783281,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「今年夏天美貌最高峰的女神」BEST9！看到她們再炎熱的暑氣都會被擊退！","createTime":"2018-08-17T12:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T05:56:57.000Z","uid":51412,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6465c48b01084eb118539d14ce8bfa59568eb2fe","tid":783281,"uid":51412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:02:14.000Z","msg":"「今年夏天美貌最高峰的女神」BEST9！看到她們再炎熱的暑氣都會被擊退！<br />\n<br />\n今年夏天大家的眼睛真的是太有福氣啦！<br />\n<br />\n夏日女團回歸大戰不只讓粉絲們有聽不完的好歌，還有數不清的美貌可以欣賞！快來看看<br />\n你們心目中的女神有沒有上榜吧！(以下數字非排名)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oy4Qiz1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Foy4Qiz1.jpg&h=d22898b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1. Red Velvet - Irene<br />\n每次回歸概念照都會美出新高度的Irene，讓人不禁納悶Irene的美貌盡頭到底在哪裡阿？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/f9J8GrR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ff9J8GrR.png&h=eea43237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. GFRIEND - 嚴智<br />\n大家的拇指公主嚴智在不知不覺中已經長大了，嬰兒肥消失之後美貌更是直線升級阿！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MqavOJW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMqavOJW.jpg&h=d5a85a9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3. TWICE - 志效<br />\n就算曬黑也毫不影響美貌的志效，深邃大眼配上黝黑的皮膚更加凸顯健康性感美！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CZN8bYp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCZN8bYp.jpg&h=784210b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4. BLACKPINK - Jennie<br />\n被封為「人間香奈兒」的Jennie，任何名牌都能輕易消化，因為外貌本身就是名品阿！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CM6tK4e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCM6tK4e.png&h=1880b5aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5. 請夏<br />\n就算只有一個人也很耀眼的女神請夏，無窮無盡的魅力多到照相機都快裝不下啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CgTI6Ok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCgTI6Ok.jpg&h=af6025f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6. gugudan - 美娜<br />\n將橘子的清爽擬人化就是我們美娜吧！看到美娜就覺得果汁美源源不絕地湧出來阿！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9VqIt9X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9VqIt9X.png&h=a26ce527&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7. Apink - 普美<br />\n靠「果汁減肥法」瘦身讓美貌瞬間衝到顛峰的普美，挺鼻再加上鵝蛋臉，太漂亮啦~<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CMaVQMi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCMaVQMi.png&h=b5b041df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n8. MAMAMOO - 頌樂<br />\n這個夏天比太陽還更耀眼的頌樂！美貌指數一再創新高，再看看這身材，太犯規了吧~<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5Cbz5IT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5Cbz5IT.png&h=3dcbc9d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n9. AOA - 雪炫<br />\n簡單的背心短褲配上雪炫的好身材就是不一樣，雪炫的美貌真的是360度零死角阿！<br />\n<br />\n看完以上，心目中的女神沒有上榜也不要灰心，快留言安利自家女神，讓大家知道這個夏<br />\n天錯過誰一定會後悔！"},{"pid":"067f6e2e5ba560b420db1bdc552ac1810abf0a61","tid":783281,"uid":34489,"like":8,"dislike":9,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:05:06.000Z","msg":"豬FD 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a68f88969dffb20865ea5a44c9cdae78e8f2eb","tid":783281,"uid":69472,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:08:10.000Z","msg":"泡菜雞po出嚟做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9564a92763fe8675837e8445a722ee05f6a063d","tid":783281,"uid":63057,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:16:27.000Z","msg":"睇到第2 umji笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美貌最高"},{"pid":"3d92aebb16e5f92640c4f0e2907e759667130a26","tid":783281,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:17:10.000Z","msg":"人造人"},{"pid":"bb2532bff211bb707a5feabc64169dad29c9e663","tid":783281,"uid":89931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:17:19.000Z","msg":"一半垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgm